data.description: Recently Built Lennar home in quiet Verandah neighborhood with community pool, playground, sand volleyball court, soccer field, and jogging trails. Great open layout, high ceilings, great natural lighting, and a lovely size kitchen island. New carpet has recently been installed, the interior walls have been repainted throughout the home, and the backyard patio has been extended.  Smart home features include a ring doorbell, smart sensors, garage door opener controlled through My Q garage app, and water turn off and and on all through the phone. Within walking distance of a brand new elementary school and only 2 miles from the high school. Make this your home today! Motivated seller!
